  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/17bb8f8b84f576722cfa336e0f29b79d.avif?t=1749365600\" width=300 height=162 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/b10dfeae86ad47fd3d6147f961c08e73.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/b10dfeae86ad47fd3d6147f961c08e73.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/b10dfeae86ad47fd3d6147f961c08e73.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death Delivery is fast paced FPS action that you can take S L O W, taking inspiration from many amazing experiences,this is ARCADE fun  that you can quickly jump into and start having pure fun,Enjoy flashy visuals and<strong> satisfying effects.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                         HARD TO MASTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/7b1f6996fd1638b4d23a5effe41b4294.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/7b1f6996fd1638b4d23a5effe41b4294.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/7b1f6996fd1638b4d23a5effe41b4294.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >rush your way into<strong> non-stop action</strong> levels without getting hit even once. brutal trial-and-error difficulty ensures that you'll master mechanics of game and will have tons of fun doing it,quick and highly replayable satisfying action with homages to classic 2000s action.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                       ⚡ Execution Finishers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/68171af6b019569010c5bedd6bee561b.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/68171af6b019569010c5bedd6bee561b.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/68171af6b019569010c5bedd6bee561b.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When enemies are weakened, get close and trigger a brutal animation-based kill. It's fast, bloody, and satisfying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                     🚨 Helmets: Unleash New Powers! 🚨</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Helmets with unique buffs and abilities to enhance your playstyle and give you the edge in every battle! ⚡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/59c09d174baa21782ae9c2821a2bcf17.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/59c09d174baa21782ae9c2821a2bcf17.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/59c09d174baa21782ae9c2821a2bcf17.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From boosting your speed during slides to extending your bullet time, each helmet offers something powerful to fit your needs. Whether you’re dashing through enemies or slowing time in the heat of battle, these helmets are your best friend!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/8279ff4219618ef72f7c34d98a616553.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/8279ff4219618ef72f7c34d98a616553.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/8279ff4219618ef72f7c34d98a616553.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip, upgrade, and dominate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the update now and find the perfect helmet to match your style. Get ready to feel the power in every helmet! 💥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/0792642fa60a36175bc46c98d2111c51.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/0792642fa60a36175bc46c98d2111c51.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/0792642fa60a36175bc46c98d2111c51.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                        FREEDOM OF STYLE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/4c5c9611183a2ba777248ef8578e433c.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/4c5c9611183a2ba777248ef8578e433c.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/4c5c9611183a2ba777248ef8578e433c.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                        🎥 Cinematic Touches</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >camera shake, time-slow effects, and dynamic angles to make every finisher feel impactful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/46bd478e35644b8ff07170cb6e6fcd67.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/46bd478e35644b8ff07170cb6e6fcd67.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/46bd478e35644b8ff07170cb6e6fcd67.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play your way! combine gunplay,melee,arms,legs and slow motion, with your creativity to get best experience and to achieve best score to unlock new levels.Its hard, but so is life of hire gun.are you up to the task?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/1fdaf7b379f5c67a4fbae0d2eee75b00.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/1fdaf7b379f5c67a4fbae0d2eee75b00.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/1fdaf7b379f5c67a4fbae0d2eee75b00.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                                         NON-LINEAR</strong> levels</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/8f9edfc16d5ffe8b76e05eef60e3eede.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/8f9edfc16d5ffe8b76e05eef60e3eede.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/8f9edfc16d5ffe8b76e05eef60e3eede.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different routes,ways,angles how you take fight is up up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/0043c6cb8f9b93cf55a418639a7f7ea3.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/0043c6cb8f9b93cf55a418639a7f7ea3.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/0043c6cb8f9b93cf55a418639a7f7ea3.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay sharp — and get ready to tear it up!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/17bb8f8b84f576722cfa336e0f29b79d.avif?t=1749365600\" width=300 height=162 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/b10dfeae86ad47fd3d6147f961c08e73.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/b10dfeae86ad47fd3d6147f961c08e73.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/b10dfeae86ad47fd3d6147f961c08e73.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death Delivery is fast paced FPS action that you can take S L O W, taking inspiration from many amazing experiences,this is ARCADE fun  that you can quickly jump into and start having pure fun,Enjoy flashy visuals and<strong> satisfying effects.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                         HARD TO MASTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/7b1f6996fd1638b4d23a5effe41b4294.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/7b1f6996fd1638b4d23a5effe41b4294.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/7b1f6996fd1638b4d23a5effe41b4294.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >rush your way into<strong> non-stop action</strong> levels without getting hit even once. brutal trial-and-error difficulty ensures that you'll master mechanics of game and will have tons of fun doing it,quick and highly replayable satisfying action with homages to classic 2000s action.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                       ⚡ Execution Finishers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/68171af6b019569010c5bedd6bee561b.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/68171af6b019569010c5bedd6bee561b.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/68171af6b019569010c5bedd6bee561b.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When enemies are weakened, get close and trigger a brutal animation-based kill. It's fast, bloody, and satisfying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                     🚨 Helmets: Unleash New Powers! 🚨</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Helmets with unique buffs and abilities to enhance your playstyle and give you the edge in every battle! ⚡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/59c09d174baa21782ae9c2821a2bcf17.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/59c09d174baa21782ae9c2821a2bcf17.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/59c09d174baa21782ae9c2821a2bcf17.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From boosting your speed during slides to extending your bullet time, each helmet offers something powerful to fit your needs. Whether you’re dashing through enemies or slowing time in the heat of battle, these helmets are your best friend!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/8279ff4219618ef72f7c34d98a616553.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/8279ff4219618ef72f7c34d98a616553.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/8279ff4219618ef72f7c34d98a616553.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip, upgrade, and dominate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the update now and find the perfect helmet to match your style. Get ready to feel the power in every helmet! 💥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/0792642fa60a36175bc46c98d2111c51.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/0792642fa60a36175bc46c98d2111c51.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/0792642fa60a36175bc46c98d2111c51.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                        FREEDOM OF STYLE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/4c5c9611183a2ba777248ef8578e433c.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/4c5c9611183a2ba777248ef8578e433c.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/4c5c9611183a2ba777248ef8578e433c.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                        🎥 Cinematic Touches</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >camera shake, time-slow effects, and dynamic angles to make every finisher feel impactful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/46bd478e35644b8ff07170cb6e6fcd67.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/46bd478e35644b8ff07170cb6e6fcd67.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/46bd478e35644b8ff07170cb6e6fcd67.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play your way! combine gunplay,melee,arms,legs and slow motion, with your creativity to get best experience and to achieve best score to unlock new levels.Its hard, but so is life of hire gun.are you up to the task?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/1fdaf7b379f5c67a4fbae0d2eee75b00.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/1fdaf7b379f5c67a4fbae0d2eee75b00.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/1fdaf7b379f5c67a4fbae0d2eee75b00.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                                         NON-LINEAR</strong> levels</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/8f9edfc16d5ffe8b76e05eef60e3eede.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/8f9edfc16d5ffe8b76e05eef60e3eede.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/8f9edfc16d5ffe8b76e05eef60e3eede.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different routes,ways,angles how you take fight is up up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/0043c6cb8f9b93cf55a418639a7f7ea3.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/0043c6cb8f9b93cf55a418639a7f7ea3.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/0043c6cb8f9b93cf55a418639a7f7ea3.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay sharp — and get ready to tear it up!</p>",
